 sation: NLnet / NGI Fediversity (funded by EU Horizon Europe)\nLocation: W
 orldwide\nAward: €5\,000 to €50\,000 per project\nDuration: Project-ba
 sed\n\nMore: https://nlnet.nl/fediversity/
